snippet.title: Punch-Out!! (Wii) - Donkey Kong [53.96]
snippet.description:
To be clear, the TAS with this strat is 52.80, so there's definitely time to be saved, I've just never been a huge fan of this fight so not itching to improve it right away.

The whiffed punch is required to get DK to do the quicker taunt at the end of phase 1 to save a few frames. The rest of the timesave comes from delaying the 3rd double star in phase 1, meaning Little Mac only has to throw 1 punch instead of 2 to trigger DK's next attack. The rest of the strat's the same as before.
